631
00:58:12,960 --> 00:58:16,000
"She’s the one who offered me that job before,"

632
00:58:16,360 --> 00:58:17,760
"the one I turned down."

633
00:58:18,280 --> 00:58:19,880
"Luckily, when I came back,"

634
00:58:19,880 --> 00:58:23,160
