to get the position again."

635
00:58:23,760 --> 00:58:25,800
"My life is finally falling into place."

636
00:58:27,600 --> 00:58:28,920
Umm, sorry.

637
00:58:29,400 --> 00:58:30,080
It’s okay.

638
